In `lib/screens/splash_screen.dart`, fix the `AnimationController` parameter from `vsync` to `vsync` (TickerProvider):

```dart
_controller = AnimationController(
  duration: const Duration(milliseconds: 2000),
  vsync: this,  // was vsync
);
```

